_______________________________________________________________________________
"Banish"        
        An expensive but powerful effect, the target of the power will be
        teleported away to otherdimensional space unless it resists the
        spell.  Such strenous mental efforts cannot be maintained long,
        however, and the target will soon return to Darkwind.  Make good
        use of the time provided to search, move on, or escape!
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  12	Potential Points:  5
 
Command:  pbanish <target>
